edu.uiuc.ncsa.qdl.state

Class AbstractSymbolTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uiuc.ncsa.qdl.state.AbstractSymbolTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SymbolTable, XMLSerializable, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SymbolStack, SymbolTableImpl

    public abstract class AbstractSymbolTable
extends Object
implements SymbolTable
    The interface for access to symbols (aka variables) in QDL. Note that this is not assumed to be namespace aware at all. It is not the task of this component to understand or resolve namespaces.

    Created by Jeff Gaynor
    on 1/21/20 at 5:04 PM
